data.description: **Seize the Moment: Unbeatable $80,000 Price Adjustment from Motivated Sellers!    Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the desirable Navy Oaks neighborhood. Built in 2018, this modern residence spans a spacious 2,361 square feet, providing ample room for comfortable living. Upon entering, the precision in craftsmanship and the presence of top-tier finishes become instantly evident.  Sunlit interiors seamlessly flow through the open-concept design, creating a welcoming and spacious atmosphere. The large kitchen showcases upgraded sea-glass countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances, and an expansive pantry—a chef's paradise. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family.  Ascend to the upper level, where the primary suite awaits with a generously-sized en-suite bathroom featuring his and hers sinks, an oversized soaking tub, and a sprawling walk-in closet.   Designed with both elegance and resilience in mind, the luxury vinyl plank flooring graces high-traffic areas, while plush carpeting in the bedrooms bestows a cozy and inviting atmosphere.  Step outside to discover a fenced-in yard, providing both tranquility and seclusion. Positioned conveniently near beaches, NAS, and shopping centers, this residence offers a lifestyle marked by both comfort and convenience.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in Navy Oaks your own.
